    <name>Beth Israel Cemetery</name>
    <description><![CDATA[1207 W. Dallas<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> 1207 W. Dallas, Houston<br/><br/><b>Marker Text:</b> Beth Israel Cemetery Established c. 1844 Historic Texas Cemetery - 2005]]></description>
    <Point><coordinates>-95.379555,29.757979,0</coordinates></Point>
